('Valencia Real Estate Consulting Group', 'Real Estate', 'English-speaking real estate consulting group specializing in helping expatriates find their dream home in Valencia, Spain. Founded by David Piccolo with over 33 years of real estate experience in both the US and Valencia. Unlike traditional Spanish realtors who only show their own listings, they operate as buyer''s consultants, meaning they can show ANY property for sale including new construction and collaborate with seller''s agents. Their fiduciary responsibility is exclusively to the buyer, not the seller. They provide personalized guidance and expert support throughout the entire home buying process, starting before clients even leave their home country. Services include property search, understanding Spanish real estate customs, investment advice, and referrals to partners throughout Spain for those considering areas outside Valencia province.', 'Calle Jacint Labaila, 5', 'Valencia', 'Valencia', '+34 669 838 760', NULL, 'https://www.valenciarealestateconsultinggroup.com', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
